HEADWORD: Difformity
<hw>Dif*form"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>difformit⟦eacute⟧</ets>. See <er>Difform</er>,
<er>Deformity</er>.]</ety> <def>Irregularity of form; diversity of form;
want of uniformity.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir T.
Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

